Rules:
- Eating, thinking, sleeping -> can do only one thing at a time
- Amount of fork = amount of philosopher
- Philosopher must pick 2 forks (right and left) in order to eat
- After philosopher has finished eating, they put the fork back to the table and start sleeping
- Once philospher awake they start thinking again
- The simulation stops when  philosopher dies of startvation

Philosopher:
- Needs to eat
- Do not communicate with each other
- Do not know if another philosoher is about to die

About program:
- Take these arguments: number_of_philosophers, time_to_die, time_to_eat, time_to_sleep, number_of_times_each_philospher_must_eat (optional argument)
- The time unit is milisecond